snippet.title: Barbie and the Magic of Pegasus - Full Game, No Commentary
snippet.description:
Michael plays "Barbie and the Magic of Pegasus", the PC game. There is no commentary for this video.

The Arglefumph logo animation at the start of this video was made by Serge Hanna. The music was made by alwaysthebutler.
